snippet.title: [S] ACT 4 ==►(1080p HD)
snippet.description:
Homestuck's first fully interactive walkaround Flash.
The Land of Wind and Shade is introduced by name as John walks around on its surface. Nanna offers some rather cryptic advice, but John's Consorts, the Salamanders, offer up plenty of information on John's planet, the Underlings he has been battling, and just how much of a fuckin' pain in the ass it is to farm these goddamn mushrooms.

===Note===
Know what else is a fuckin' pain in the ass? Recording heavy interactive flashes!
I missed two things in the flash so I added them at the end.
Trickster mode is ineffective!

Song:
"Doctor"
By George Buzinkai

Page:
http://www.mspaintadventures.com/?s=6&p=003258
